[Enhanced Chaperone Capacity]\n    AT --> AU[Improved Protein Folding]\n    \n    AP --> AV[Disulfide Bond Formation]\n    AV --> AU\n    \n    AQ --> AW{ERAD Pathway?}\n    AW -->|Recognition| AX[Misfolded Protein Detection]\n    AX --> AY[Retrotranslocation]\n    AY --> AZ[Ubiquitination]\n    AZ --> BA[/Proteasomal Degradation/]\n    \n    AR --> BB[Phospholipid Synthesis]\n    AS --> BB\n    BB --> BC[ER Membrane Expansion]\n    BC --> BD[Increased ER Volume]\n    \n    AU --> BE{Protein Folding Success?}\n    BE -->|Properly Folded| BF[Secretory Pathway]\n    BE -->|Still Misfolded| AW\n    \n    BF --> BG[ER Exit]\n    BA --> BH[Reduced ER Load]\n    \n    BG --> BI{ER Stress Resolution?}\n    BH --> BI\n    BD --> BI\n    \n    BI -->|Stress Reduced| BJ[BiP Available]\n    BI -->|Stress Persists| F\n    \n    BJ --> BK[/BiP Rebinding to Ire1/]\n    BK --> BL[Ire1 Inactivation]\n    BL --> BM[/HAC1 Splicing Stops/]\n    \n    BM --> BN[/Hac1p Degradation?/]\n    BN -->|Short Half-life| BO[Rapid Turnover]\n    BO --> BP[UPR Shutdown]\n    \n    BP --> BQ{Cell Fate?}\n    BQ -->|Stress Resolved| BR(\\1)\n    BQ -->|Chronic Stress| BS(\\1)\n    \n    BR --> BT[Normal ER Function]\n    BS --> BU[Cell Death]\n    \n    AJ --> BV{Hac1p Regulation?}\n    BV -->|Phosphorylation| BW[Activity Modulation]\n    BV -->|Degradation Signals| BX[Protein Stability]\n    \n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n    style A fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style B fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style C fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style D fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style E fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style F fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style G fill:#000000,color:#fff\n    style H fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style I fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style J fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style K fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff\n    style L fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style M fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n   