  "scientificAccuracy": "This flowchart is based on extensive peer-reviewed literature on yeast UPR, including studies on Ire1 structure and function, HAC1 mRNA splicing, and downstream gene regulation. The pathway components, regulatory mechanisms, and logic gates have been validated against primary research sources. The yeast UPR serves as the paradigm for understanding ER stress responses in all eukaryotes.",
